A OpenGL clone of the popular Pong game.
Created with Qt4 and OpenGL.

Build Instructions (Unix/Shell):
- cd /into/project/directory/
- qmake
- make
- ./glPong

Game Keys:
- Space = Pause/Start the game
- Enter = Start ball movement
- A/Y = Move player 1 up/down
- Cursor Up/Down = move player 2 up/down
- F = Toggle between fullscreen and normal mode
- ESC = Quit game

Future Plans:
- Classes for player and ball
- Slider to change ball speed ingame
- Server/Client architecture to play via internet
- Hit sounds